{"tid":1304560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日沙田到底係做乜","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T03:08:07.000Z","uid":275787,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"408579d4bd3a3d6de6ebf58222f1614d8751d513","tid":1304560,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係五大訴求</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好似係 除非唔係</span><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆：<br />\n可以做<br />\n當回血都得<br />\n發洩渠道係必須嘅<br />\n但係連儂牆內容集中番文宣會好啲<br />\n（我知有 不過有啲巴打好似唔知連儂牆有文宣..？）<br />\n<br />\n光復十八區嘅時候<br />\n順便有埋七大訴求會唔會好啲<br />\n有人覺得光復會失焦<br />\n<br />\n然後 長期都要有七大訴求置頂<br />\n打飛機嘅po（寶礦力之類）如果見到已經有就唔好再開<br />\n<br />\n有啲巴打覺得連儂牆無謂<br />\n有啲覺得光復十八區失焦<br />\n冇問題<br />\n但係亦都希望可以屌細力少少<br />\n相信下佢地係記得七大訴求好冇<br />\n唔好下下都覺得冇用<br />\n要樣樣嘢都試下先會搵到方向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（頭盔）鳩up</span>"},{"pid":"b6c74349678a0d41ebed2d06397b20e12fb23661","tid":1304560,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:55:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重申抗爭所堅持之五大訴求:<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權<br />\n五、實行雙真普選</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd0f4ac751d4053fe5be7ead2df638fd7f4ccaba","tid":1304560,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"連儂一係開創意台？"},{"pid":"a2372d453e2520aa6b9898c443ef89c57eec7779","tid":1304560,"uid":269965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a0fd8b95d0e710ade1e749d6bbf7bc96acb697","tid":1304560,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed52326156